WEBVTT

00:09.031 --> 00:11.585
Okay.

00:12.908 --> 00:15.179
Oh, chérie. So beautiful.

00:15.204 --> 00:17.719
Just gorgeous.

00:17.966 --> 00:19.672
Clip the bunny.

00:21.000 --> 00:27.074
